snippet.title: Why Amber Heard is the WORST advocate for Domestic Violence Victims
snippet.description:
Hi guy's and gal's, so, here is the video I have been wanting to do for a while, I created this video because like many, I'm tired of watching Amber Heard continue to use her accusations of Domestic Violence against Johnny Depp, even though she dropped the charges, to keep herself in the spotlight. 

I'm passionate about this as she is taking the attention away and making it more difficult for real domestic violence victims to speak out, especially when all she is teaching them is to drop the claim and demand money. 

This is really to provide Amber Heard supporters with the facts and court documents, as they do not seem to be well known to her fans. 

Here are the links to all of the articles, statements and court documents that I used throughout this video: 

Amber Heard Court filling for divorce - http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3609754/Battle-begins-Johnny-Depp-s-400M-fortune-Pirates-Caribbean-star-asks-judge-reject-Amber-Heard-s-request-spousal-support-NO-pre-nup.html

Amber Heard expenses form: http://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/amber-heards-44k-monthly-expenses-8093340

Laura Wasser Declaration and Amber Heard Abuse allegation documents - http://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/read-full-explosive-amber-heard-8070432

Amber Heard and Johnny Depp joint statement - 
http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/amber-heard-and-johnny-depp-divorce-settlement-read-their-statement-in-full-a7194266.html

Amber Heard Instagram re-share: www.instagram.com/amberheard

Amber Heard Allure Article: 
https://www.allure.com/story/amber-heard-cover-story-december-2017

Amber Heard Domestic Violence arrest: 
http://www.tmz.com/2016/06/07/amber-heard-domestic-violence-arrest-partner-tasya-van-ree/

Amber Heard Mugshot 2009:
https://jambernews.wordpress.com/tag/mugshot/


Amber Heard PornHub video - pornhub

Johnny Depp Witness list: https://www.express.co.uk/celebrity-news/698167/Johnny-Depp-has-TWENTY-witnesses-to-help-prove-he-didn-t-assault-Amber-Heard

Seriously, the information is out there for everybody to read, all you have to do is look.
